long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: With the Teem Google extension, any employee at an organization Powered by Teem can reap the benefits of booking with Teem without leaving their existing work calendar behind. Set up your meetings per usual: invite participants, select the best date and time based on your participants’ calendars. Then, using the extension, choose the room(s) that work best for your meeting based on location, capacity, and amenity filters.
